# ListCard(firstNameString, employees, locations)
-```
{
    "type": "AdaptiveCard",
    "$schema": "http://adaptivecards.io/schemas/adaptive-card.json",
    "version": "1.2",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "${firstNameString} and **${employees.count - 3} others** are on client work${TimeInfo(turn.formatDate)}.",
            "wrap": true
        },
        {
            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "You can narrow your search by specifying an office location.\n",
            "wrap": true
        },
        {
            "type": "ActionSet",
            "actions": [
                {
                    "type": "Action.Submit",
                    "title": "Show All [${employees.count}]",
                    "data": {
                        "intent": "GetPeopleOnClientWork",
                        "location": "All"
                    }
                },
                ${join(select(subArray(locations, 0, 5), location => LocationButton(skill, location, employees)), ',')}
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "ActionSet",
            "actions": [
                ${join(select(subArray(locations, 5, count(locations)), location => LocationButton(skill, location, employees)), ',')}
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

# TimeInfo(date)
- ${if(date != null, TimeString(date), '')}

# TimeString(date)
-``` on ${date}```

# LocationButton(skill, location, employees)
-``` 
{
    "type": "Action.Submit",
    "title": "${location} [${Count(location, employees)}]",
    "data": {
        "intent": "GetPeopleOnClientWork",
        "location": "${location}"
    }
}
```

# Count(location, employees)
- ${count(where(employees, employee => employee.defaultSite.name == location))}


